_sText:
Hello!

I give you a map for the joint passage.

On this map are located all the complexity of the complex, from the easiest to the most complex. There are both sovmesnoe passage and a single passage.

There are 30 new levels on the map.

With the passage of all 30 levels, there is a bonus on the card, when it passes you will be available 1337 bonus for skill players. If you pass 1337 bonus, then you will open the skins room, where you can take yourself a skin from the game Mirror's edge.

Throughout the map there is music accompaniment with the name of the song on the center of the screen. Some music needs to be taken with the help of difficulties, so you do not get bored.

At the end of the map there is music that you can switch and the music will not overlap and will not be bounced, all music will turn on after 2 seconds.

At the passage of 1337 bonus plays special music, which is like.

The design and textures on the map look good and will not get on your nerves.

Throughout the map there is good lighting, there are no bugs with textures.

Video on the passage is not ready yet, but soon I will make a video of the map.

I really hope that you will enjoy playing on my map!

Have a good game!
